15:15.994 --> 15:18.061
That was easy.

15:18.063 --> 15:21.030
[GRUNTS]

15:21.032 --> 15:22.866
Okay.

15:22.868 --> 15:25.068
All right, Nick.

15:25.070 --> 15:27.270
All right, you're fine.

15:27.272 --> 15:28.705
You're fine.

15:28.807 --> 15:30.440
You're fine.

15:30.442 --> 15:37.514
<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:40.352 --> 15:42.886
[GRUNTS]

15:42.888 --> 15:46.523
<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:46.525 --> 15:49.292
[MOANING LOUDLY]

15:49.294 --> 15:56.332
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:01.059 --> 16:04.520
- Looks dead to me.
- Less paperwork if he's dead.

16:06.279 --> 16:07.545
- [GRUNTS]
- Oh, shit!

16:07.548 --> 16:09.631
Don't move, sir, don't move!

16:09.633 --> 16:11.800
[SIREN WAILS]

16:14.638 --> 16:16.471
What the hell is this?

16:16.473 --> 16:18.700
Put your guns back in your pants.

16:21.478 --> 16:24.312
