17:41.725 --> 17:45.260
Hey! Make sure you keep him alive,

17:45.262 --> 17:47.195
or I promise you, it's your balls.

17:47.197 --> 17:50.365
Hey, what about me,
huh? I've been violated!

17:50.367 --> 17:54.144
Take her home. No stops along the way.

17:54.147 --> 17:55.746
What do you want?

17:55.749 --> 17:58.839
Detective, ma'am, look,
the guy's been shot.

17:58.842 --> 18:00.708
He's had a heart attack,
maybe two heart attacks.

18:00.710 --> 18:03.378
- The chances he makes it...
- He'll live.

18:03.380 --> 18:05.441
He always does.

18:07.417 --> 18:11.052
So many lights, so many people.

18:11.054 --> 18:12.921
I'll never find him.

18:12.923 --> 18:15.323
Yes, you will! Because you have to!

18:15.325 --> 18:19.260
