18:26.403 --> 18:29.270
Jeez, I thought I was having a bad day.

18:29.272 --> 18:31.439
<i>♪ ♪</i>

18:31.441 --> 18:34.909
Okay, you two look busy.

18:34.911 --> 18:37.812
<i>♪ ♪</i>

18:37.814 --> 18:40.481
Can you see me?

18:40.483 --> 18:42.750
Yerks!

18:42.752 --> 18:47.555
Whoa! There must be an
easier way to order a drink!

18:47.557 --> 18:49.707
I think you're going the wrong way!

18:49.710 --> 18:51.176
Hey, watch it, pal!

18:51.179 --> 18:55.781
[TIRES SCREECHING, ENGINE REVVING]

18:55.784 --> 18:57.564
Whoa, looks like someone's got a lot

18:57.567 --> 19:00.501
