19:00.503 --> 19:02.937
He's close, Haley. I can feel it.

19:02.939 --> 19:05.571
[SNIFFS] Actually, I can smell it.

19:05.574 --> 19:07.942
[SIREN WAILING]

19:07.944 --> 19:09.444
He's got a vest!

19:09.446 --> 19:13.014
- What the...
