19:13.016 --> 19:14.782
[SHOUTS INDISTINCTLY]

19:14.784 --> 19:17.986
[PADDLES CHARGING]

19:17.988 --> 19:20.521
Clear! Three, two, one!

19:20.523 --> 19:22.824
It's like cooking a steak!

19:22.826 --> 19:24.325
Give him another!

19:24.327 --> 19:27.644
BOTH: Three, two, one!

19:27.647 --> 19:29.551
She said if we lose him, it's our balls.

19:29.554 --> 19:31.184
Do you think she meant
that literally or like...

19:31.186 --> 19:32.666
Like a figure of speech or something?

19:32.669 --> 19:33.968
We're not gonna lose him!

19:33.970 --> 19:35.340
- Huh?
- Pure adrenaline.

19:35.343 --> 19:38.940
I got to admit, I've
always wanted to do this.

19:38.942 --> 19:43.878
[GASPS, SCREAMING]

19:43.880 --> 19:47.715
Morphine! 20 migs stat!

19:47.717 --> 19:52.453
- [CAR HORN HONKING]
- [LAUGHING] Whoo!

19:52.455 --> 19:57.725
[LAUGHING] Aaah!

19:57.727 --> 19:59.727
Oh, that's warm.

19:59.729 --> 20:03.144
<i>[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]</i>

20:03.147 --> 20:06.014
Nitroglycerin!

20:06.017 --> 20:09.337
34 migs. Ah...

20:09.339 --> 20:13.174
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:13.176 --> 20:15.343
Oh, yeah.

20:15.345 --> 20:17.011
That's it.

20:17.013 --> 20:19.013
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:19.015 --> 20:22.383
[SIREN WAILING]

20:22.385 --> 20:27.055
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:29.359 --> 20:33.094
Hey, mister! Come on, snap out of it!

20:33.096 --> 20:35.830
[SIREN WAILING]

20:35.832 --> 20:38.099
[GRUNTS]

20:38.101 --> 20:40.668
Whoa! [LAUGHING] You can see me!

20:40.670 --> 20:42.246
What the hell?

20:42.249 --> 20:44.405
Yeah, you ain't quite
what I expected either.

20:44.407 --> 20:49.010
I guess we get what we get,
and we don't get upset, right?

20:49.012 --> 20:51.996
Oh, boy. Well, here goes nothing.

20:51.999 --> 20:55.850
I'm Happy!

20:55.852 --> 20:57.552
♪ The happy horse, horse, horse ♪

20:57.554 --> 20:59.353
