20:59.355 --> 21:01.622
♪ It's plain to see it's fun to be Happy ♪

21:01.624 --> 21:02.629
[NEIGHING]

21:02.632 --> 21:04.054
♪ The happy horse, horse, horse ♪

21:04.057 --> 21:05.764
♪ So full of love, of course, of course ♪

21:05.767 --> 21:09.029
♪ It's time to be carefree,
so come with me, Happy! ♪

21:09.032 --> 21:10.631
[HOOVES CLOMPING]

21:10.633 --> 21:12.793
Here it comes!

21:12.796 --> 21:15.236
Here comes the fun! Are you ready?

21:15.238 --> 21:17.605
- I'm ready!
- Here it comes!

21:17.607 --> 21:19.098
♪ Clippety-clop, flippety-flop ♪

21:19.101 --> 21:20.508
♪ We got no time to mope and mop ♪

21:20.510 --> 21:22.074
♪ Let's ride the magic rainbow ♪

21:22.077 --> 21:23.878
♪ Right to the tippy,
tippy, tippy, tippy... ♪

21:23.880 --> 21:25.379
Stop!

21:25.381 --> 21:28.216
I'm hallucinating. Nitro.

21:28.218 --> 21:30.718
Go away. Ah...

21:30.720 --> 21:33.087
But... but I-I got stuff to tell you!

21:33.089 --> 21:34.399
<i>Mucho</i> important stuff!

21:34.402 --> 21:35.990
Shh.

21:35.992 --> 21:37.759
I don't talk to pink elephants.

21:37.761 --> 21:40.582
What, are you color
blind? I ain't pink, pal.

21:40.585 --> 21:43.464
And elephants have trunks!
Do you see any luggage?

21:43.466 --> 21:44.785
[CHUCKLES]

21:44.788 --> 21:46.421
Kill this thing any way you can.

21:46.424 --> 21:48.503
- They can't see me.
- What... I...

21:48.505 --> 21:50.004
Only you can see me.

21:50.007 --> 21:51.672
- Ah...
- Aah!

21:51.674 --> 21:55.575
- Aah.
- Ah...

21:55.578 --> 22:00.014
Look, asshole, I'm gonna take a nap now.

22:00.016 --> 22:02.450
When I wake up, I want you to...

22:02.452 --> 22:06.496
No, no, don't go. Not
yet! Haley needs us!

22:08.387 --> 22:13.194
<i>♪ ♪</i>

22:13.196 --> 22:15.696
Well, usually you're a great source

22:15.698 --> 22:17.698
of information, but this time

22:17.700 --> 22:19.700
<i>I'm afraid you're mistaken.</i>

22:19.702 --> 22:22.503
<i>My favorite nephew, he's
currently en route from Italy.</i>

22:22.505 --> 22:24.639
Maybe he was yesterday.

22:24.641 --> 22:26.707
Right now he's in the county morgue.

22:26.709 --> 22:30.478
And Nick Sax has got
his fat, grubby fingers

22:30.480 --> 22:32.346
on my password.

22:32.348 --> 22:35.817
Meredith! Your father's on the TV again!

22:35.819 --> 22:37.949
That evil bastard is so handsome.

22:37.952 --> 22:40.345
You know, I can tell
you're real broken up

22:40.348 --> 22:42.957
<i>about losing four nephews
in one night, Blue.</i>

22:42.959 --> 22:45.259
Maybe I should give you
a little time to process.

22:45.261 --> 22:48.996
How very compassionate of
you, Detective McCarthy...

22:48.998 --> 22:51.799
and during the holiday season.

22:53.336 --> 22:55.169
Gerry.

22:55.171 --> 22:57.738
Gerry, pay attention
to Whiskers, please.

22:57.740 --> 22:59.273
[DOG YELPS]

22:59.275 --> 23:00.590
Scratch him.

23:00.593 --> 23:03.211
It's the antlers, dear. He hates them.

23:03.213 --> 23:05.546
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:05.548 --> 23:07.548
[DOG BARKS]

23:07.550 --> 23:09.717
<i>Sax should be at General.</i>

23:09.719 --> 23:12.620
I will be there when he wakes
up and have a little chat.

23:12.622 --> 23:16.457
<i>And I hope that conversation
goes very, very well.</i>

23:16.459 --> 23:21.262
The thought that that swollen
troglodyte might actually die

23:21.264 --> 23:23.129
before I get what I need out of him...

23:23.132 --> 23:24.966
<i>Well, I'm sure you understand.</i>

23:24.968 --> 23:28.870
<i>It won't be you that I
come to vent my spleen on.</i>

23:28.872 --> 23:32.613
<i>How is your ma? Silly, fragile old thing.</i>

23:32.616 --> 23:34.650
<i>She been taking her medication?</i>

23:34.653 --> 23:38.045
My daughter doesn't care. She
doesn't give a damn about...

23:38.047 --> 23:39.614
She...

23:41.017 --> 23:43.417
Meredith?

23:43.419 --> 23:45.453
- Meredith?
<i>- He'll talk.</i>

23:45.455 --> 23:48.689
There's something you're
not telling me, Blue.

23:48.691 --> 23:50.391
<i>I mean, first, the old Don dies</i>

23:50.393 --> 23:51.726
<i>on the other side of the world.</i>

23:51.728 --> 23:52.754
<i>Then 24 hours later,</i>

23:52.757 --> 23:54.995
<i>there's four dead
Scaramuccis in Brooklyn.</i>

23:54.998 --> 23:56.269
What's going on out there?

23:56.272 --> 24:00.067
<i>Tell your ma I said she has
to start taking her pills.</i>

24:00.069 --> 24:02.069
I can see where you get
your stubborn streak.

24:02.071 --> 24:03.971
[DOG BARKS]

24:03.973 --> 24:05.039
[PHONE CLATTERS]

24:05.041 --> 24:07.608
- [CHUCKLES]
- [PHONE DIALING]

24:07.610 --> 24:09.543
<i>[LINE TRILLING]</i>

24:09.545 --> 24:11.245
Gerry, little angel.

24:11.247 --> 24:12.713
Yes, Papa?

24:12.715 --> 24:14.293
I don't want to tell you again.

24:14.296 --> 24:16.229
If Whiskers won't stop scratching,

24:16.232 --> 24:19.220
I'm gonna have to put him on the fire.

24:19.222 --> 24:22.056
And that'll be four dogs we've
gone through in one year...

24:22.058 --> 24:26.329
Socks, J. Edgar Woofer,
Professor Buttons,

24:26.332 --> 24:29.463
and now... and now Whiskers.

24:29.465 --> 24:32.433
So, please, little...

24:32.435 --> 24:35.236
<i>♪ ♪</i>

24:35.238 --> 24:39.473
- Smoothie. Happy holidays.
<i>- [WOMAN SCREAMING]</i>

24:39.475 --> 24:41.242
[TOOL WHIRRING]

24:41.244 --> 24:44.745
And a happy holidays to you, Mr. Blue.

24:44.747 --> 24:47.114
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

24:47.116 --> 24:52.119
39 inches, 47 pounds,
blood type O negative.

24:52.121 --> 24:54.055
This backpack she had
on... What color was it?

24:54.057 --> 24:55.523
I told you. Pink.

24:55.525 --> 24:57.124
Pink, right, right.

24:57.126 --> 24:59.393
Would you say, like,
Pepto or more of a pastel?

24:59.395 --> 25:02.663
It was pink. <i>Pink</i> pink,
with Wishees all over it.

25:02.665 --> 25:07.335
Wishees. Kids love
that shit, don't they?

25:07.337 --> 25:10.604
I printed her myself two years ago.

25:10.606 --> 25:13.035
Printed her? And the father?

25:13.038 --> 25:14.729
It's just me and my daughter.

25:14.732 --> 25:16.058
Got everything we need

25:16.061 --> 25:17.510
to start the investigation on Ashley.

25:17.512 --> 25:20.247
Haley!

25:20.249 --> 25:23.784
Haley Hansen.

25:23.786 --> 25:25.941
I want to speak to Captain Rollins.

25:25.944 --> 25:27.477
Rollins?

25:27.480 --> 25:31.791
And if he's not here, Burns.
Tell him it's Amanda Hansen.

25:31.794 --> 25:35.463
Listen, I know this is tough.

25:35.465 --> 25:37.698
But we're on it.

25:37.700 --> 25:40.868
Go home. Get some sleep if you can.

25:40.870 --> 25:43.471
And I have someone you
<i>can</i> talk to in the morning.

25:43.473 --> 25:46.374
<i>[SOMBER MUSIC]</i>

25:46.376 --> 25:53.581
<i>♪ ♪</i>

25:55.885 --> 25:58.919
[MONITOR BEEPING]

25:58.921 --> 26:01.922
<i>[UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYING ON TELEVISION]</i>

26:01.924 --> 26:03.724
<i>♪ ♪</i>

26:03.726 --> 26:06.193
<i>[MAN LAUGHING ON TELEVISION]</i>

26:06.195 --> 26:09.363
I died.

26:09.365 --> 26:10.730
I did it.

26:10.733 --> 26:12.366
<i>♪ ♪</i>

26:12.368 --> 26:15.336
I really did it.

26:15.338 --> 26:16.837
And I'm in hell.

26:16.839 --> 26:19.507
<i>Not one wish, not two
wishes, but three...</i>

26:19.509 --> 26:21.629
You should be so lucky.

26:23.646 --> 26:26.547
- Oh, I bet that feels good, huh?
- Eh, nothing.

26:26.549 --> 26:28.682
Massive cardiac arrest.

26:28.684 --> 26:31.452
Point-blank bullet impact, upper torso.

26:31.454 --> 26:33.888
I've had hangovers worse than this.

26:33.890 --> 26:35.289
<i>[PA BEEPS]</i>

26:35.291 --> 26:38.192
[WHEEZING]

26:38.194 --> 26:40.561
- I'm an invalid.
- What?

26:40.563 --> 26:43.631
I'm an invalid. Open up a window.

26:43.633 --> 26:45.833
Window!

26:45.835 --> 26:47.601
It's against the law
to smoke in a hospital.

26:47.603 --> 26:48.969
You know that, don't you?

26:48.971 --> 26:51.939
Get it in gear. Open
up a window, will you?

26:53.076 --> 26:55.551
Not that window. No, no, no! No, no, no!

26:55.554 --> 26:57.387
Close! Close it!

26:57.390 --> 26:59.321
Lucky for me, she opened that window.

26:59.324 --> 27:03.050
I was about to turn into
a blueberry horse-sicle!

27:03.052 --> 27:04.837
[SNEEZES] Excuse me.

27:04.840 --> 27:06.554
I'm pretty sure I told you to fuck off.

27:06.556 --> 27:08.391
Oh, you did... a few times.

27:08.394 --> 27:10.082
Not you.

27:12.595 --> 27:14.228
TV's off, Nick.

27:14.230 --> 27:16.464
Yeah, I know.

27:16.466 --> 27:19.233
Meredith...

27:19.235 --> 27:20.734
what are you here for?

27:23.973 --> 27:26.860
[CHUCKLES] Nick Sax. [SMACKS LIPS]

27:26.863 --> 27:29.343
Hard to believe this piece
of shit in front of me

27:29.345 --> 27:31.846
used to be the best detective
in the whole department.

27:31.848 --> 27:34.748
Yeah, well, I was a real hero.

27:34.750 --> 27:36.519
You were mine.

27:38.821 --> 27:40.788
Wife of yours was smart
to get out when she did.

27:40.790 --> 27:42.423
Come on, you didn't come here
to go there. Don't go there.

27:42.425 --> 27:44.158
Boy, she's a regular Good Time Pam.

27:44.160 --> 27:46.387
- Shut up!
- [CUP CLATTERS]

27:48.264 --> 27:50.664
There's something wrong with you.

27:50.666 --> 27:52.902
You have no idea.

27:52.905 --> 27:55.136
Why couldn't you have just
left me out in the street?

27:55.138 --> 27:57.207
Why do you think you're here?

27:57.210 --> 28:00.011
- Here?
- Huh?

28:00.014 --> 28:03.344
Yeah, General.

28:03.346 --> 28:06.614
Some pension. Get shot just
going about your business,

28:06.616 --> 28:09.183
and the best thing they
can do is a Mob hospital.

28:09.185 --> 28:12.686
Think I still got some of
your business on my shoe.

28:12.688 --> 28:15.389
You know, I know what
Disco Mikey told you.

28:15.391 --> 28:16.441
You're in deep shit.

28:16.444 --> 28:19.298
You're in deep Bandini,
Nick. That means a bad word.

28:19.301 --> 28:22.269
I have no idea what
you're talking about.

28:22.272 --> 28:25.299
Mikey gave you a
password meant for Blue.

28:25.301 --> 28:28.636
Dumb kid ran into you before
he had a chance to deliver it.

28:28.638 --> 28:31.705
I think you know what they'll
do to get it out of you.

28:31.707 --> 28:33.674
Unless you tell me first.

28:33.676 --> 28:35.376
<i>Orderly with wheelchair
to second floor...</i>

28:35.378 --> 28:36.410
Password?

28:36.412 --> 28:38.840
Oh! Oh I know! Open sesame!

28:38.843 --> 28:41.213
Seriously?

28:41.216 --> 28:44.269
- Listen to me.
- Go.

28:44.272 --> 28:47.287
I think Blue hired you
to kill his nephews.

28:47.290 --> 28:49.657
Mikey just ended up in the
wrong place at the wrong time.

28:49.659 --> 28:52.824
I think there is a goddamn
underworld civil war brewing,

28:52.827 --> 28:54.328
and you've managed
to land your sorry ass

28:54.330 --> 28:55.394
right in the middle of it.

28:55.397 --> 28:56.796
I think I can still get you out,

28:56.799 --> 28:59.699
but you have to tell me what you know.

28:59.702 --> 29:02.570
[SIGHS]

29:02.572 --> 29:06.040
What I know?

29:06.042 --> 29:08.375
People suck, I don't pay my income tax,

29:08.377 --> 29:10.377
and I no longer feel
dirty when I touch myself,

29:10.379 --> 29:12.112
but beyond that, it
just seems pretty clear

29:12.114 --> 29:13.747
that whoever knows this alleged password

29:13.749 --> 29:16.584
is as good as dead or worse.

29:16.586 --> 29:19.687
That's about it.

29:19.689 --> 29:22.256
Oh, Meredith, you're
such a pain in the ass.

29:22.258 --> 29:24.124
Ah, look, you deserve better than that.

29:24.126 --> 29:25.726
Thanks for coming. I appreciate that.

29:25.728 --> 29:28.295
And I will tell you this...

29:28.297 --> 29:31.265
get the hell out of here.

29:31.267 --> 29:33.267
"Comprendo"? It's <i>сomprende.</i>

29:33.269 --> 29:35.436
- It's Spanish.
- I know it's Spanish!

29:35.438 --> 29:37.938
<i>[PA BEEPS]</i>

29:37.940 --> 29:39.807
<i>Nurse Peduto to outpatient...</i>

29:39.809 --> 29:41.742
All right, then.

29:41.744 --> 29:43.944
<i>[SOMBER MUSIC]</i>

29:43.946 --> 29:45.646
It is what it is.

29:45.648 --> 29:47.815
It sure ain't what it ain't!

29:47.817 --> 29:50.484
Oh, about time she left. What a charmer.

29:50.486 --> 29:52.386
Look, I don't want to
speak out of school, Nick,

29:52.388 --> 29:54.788
but I think she might
have a thing for you!

29:56.359 --> 29:59.293
Wait a minute, were you two...

29:59.295 --> 30:01.061
[GAGGING]

30:01.063 --> 30:02.605
Oh, I'm gonna lose my lunch.

30:02.608 --> 30:05.142
It's the oxycodone.

30:05.145 --> 30:07.907
[INHALES DEEPLY] Pull it together, Sax.

30:07.910 --> 30:09.970
You're hallucinating. That's bad.

30:09.972 --> 30:13.073
It's some kind of reaction.

30:13.075 --> 30:14.754
Who are you talking to, Nick?

30:14.757 --> 30:17.311
You know, I used to know a
guy who would talk to himself,

30:17.313 --> 30:19.480
and he ended up in a funny farm.

30:19.482 --> 30:21.035
He's like cuckoo, you know?

30:21.038 --> 30:24.657
[BLUBBERING CRAZILY] Cuckoo!

30:24.660 --> 30:27.021
So... you're some kind of manifestation

30:27.023 --> 30:28.622
of my subconscious, right?

30:28.624 --> 30:31.840
Yeah, you lost me at "so..."

30:31.843 --> 30:33.994
Something about a submarine sandwich?

30:33.996 --> 30:37.131
<i>[ODD DARK MUSIC]</i>

30:37.133 --> 30:39.667
Breathe, breathe.

30:39.669 --> 30:41.191
Okay, breathe.

30:41.194 --> 30:45.113
Five, four, three, two...

30:45.116 --> 30:46.716
one.

30:48.944 --> 30:51.324
This is no time for
hide-and-seek, Nick...

30:51.327 --> 30:52.560
Even though I love it.

30:52.563 --> 30:55.149
Besides, peeking is cheating.

30:55.151 --> 30:57.985
- You're not real.
- Of course not.

30:57.987 --> 31:00.120
I'm an imaginary friend.

31:00.122 --> 31:02.790
My imagination is very limited.

31:02.792 --> 31:05.693
It usually involves
inflicting pain in ways

31:05.695 --> 31:07.728
that may not have occurred to most.

31:07.730 --> 31:10.698
[LAUGHING] You're funny, Nick.

31:10.700 --> 31:12.700
But I ain't <i>your</i> imaginary friend.

31:12.702 --> 31:13.867
I don't even want to think

31:13.870 --> 31:15.230
about what that would look like.

31:15.233 --> 31:17.538
I'm Haley's imaginary friend!

31:17.540 --> 31:19.873
- Right.
- Haley's a little girl, Nick.

31:19.875 --> 31:22.637
The sweetest, most adorable
little girl in the whole world,

31:22.640 --> 31:24.324
but... but she's in real bad trouble,

31:24.327 --> 31:27.547
and you're the only one
that can help me save her!

31:27.550 --> 31:30.718
[ELEVATOR BELL DINGS]

31:30.720 --> 31:33.721
<i>[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]</i>

31:33.723 --> 31:40.761
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:47.670 --> 31:51.038
[ELEVATOR BELL DINGS]

31:51.040 --> 31:53.674
[CHUCKLES] No exit this way, Nick.

31:53.676 --> 31:58.245
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:58.247 --> 32:00.948
Jesus, that was a bad one.
Damn pills are gonna kill me.

32:00.950 --> 32:07.988
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:09.358 --> 32:11.191
All right. We got company, Nick.

32:11.193 --> 32:13.730
- And he's back!
- Some real creepazoids!

32:13.733 --> 32:15.060
Hey, if you want to be useful,

32:15.063 --> 32:16.664
why don't you tell me
how many I'm dealing with?

32:16.666 --> 32:21.058
Okay, it's one, two,
three, four, uh, five.

32:21.061 --> 32:23.962
- Are you sure about that?
- Uh-huh.

32:23.965 --> 32:27.174
So five. I've done five. I can do five.

32:31.080 --> 32:33.480
[GROWLS]

32:33.482 --> 32:36.083
Here they come, here
they come, here they come!

32:36.085 --> 32:38.318
[CHUCKLES]

32:38.320 --> 32:39.582
[THUD, CLATTER]

32:39.585 --> 32:40.756
Uh-oh.

32:42.532 --> 32:45.901
<i>[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]</i>

32:47.263 --> 32:50.797
[HYDRAULICS WHIRRING]

32:50.799 --> 32:53.901
[SNAPPING FINGERS]

32:53.903 --> 32:55.302
Ticktock, time to rock.

32:55.304 --> 32:59.373
[GROANING]

32:59.375 --> 33:02.776
Oh, that's not gonna do.

33:02.778 --> 33:05.212
Hey! Hey! Hey!

33:05.214 --> 33:08.048
- [GROANING]
- Hold on.

33:08.050 --> 33:11.485
[SHOUTING]

33:11.487 --> 33:13.153
That's better.

33:13.155 --> 33:14.584
Whoo.

33:14.587 --> 33:17.198
- Some help you turned out to be.
- No offense, buddy,

33:17.201 --> 33:18.891
but I don't see how
we're gonna save Haley

33:18.894 --> 33:20.800
if you keep fainting at
the first sign of trouble!

33:20.802 --> 33:22.763
- Why are you whispering?
- Tut tut.

33:22.766 --> 33:23.685
Okay.

33:23.688 --> 33:25.588
Drug-induced dementia is a luxury

33:25.591 --> 33:27.990
that you will no longer get to enjoy.

33:27.993 --> 33:32.623
I am going to need your
complete focus and attention.

33:34.776 --> 33:36.342
Smoothie?

33:36.345 --> 33:38.979
Clearly, my reputation precedes me.

33:38.981 --> 33:40.814
Well, I heard you like
to get pee-peed on,

33:40.816 --> 33:42.115
if that's what you mean.

33:42.118 --> 33:44.159
- [STIFLED LAUGHTER]
- Thanks for the cosign.

33:44.162 --> 33:45.913
Hey, there's nothing
wrong with it, no shame.

33:45.915 --> 33:47.794
I hear a lot of people
are into that thing.

33:47.797 --> 33:50.966
Aah! Scat video!

33:50.969 --> 33:53.162
- I beg your pardon?
- [BREATHING HEAVILY]

33:53.165 --> 33:55.362
Nothing? What?

33:55.364 --> 33:57.631
Look, asshole, let's get this over with.

33:57.633 --> 33:59.138
You want Disco Mikey's password.

33:59.141 --> 34:01.200
Oh, I'll get that. Believe me.

34:01.203 --> 34:02.232
Yeah, of course you will.

34:02.235 --> 34:04.373
I'm a tough nut, but
you'll crack it, all right.

34:04.376 --> 34:05.806
Why don't we just cut out the middleman

34:05.808 --> 34:07.007
and just get down to it, huh?

34:07.009 --> 34:08.170
I'll spill the beans.

34:08.172 --> 34:10.043
I got no illusions that
it'll buy me a quick death,

34:10.045 --> 34:11.404
but I mean, what the hell?

34:11.407 --> 34:13.623
We all got places to go, people to meet.

34:13.626 --> 34:15.525
I couldn't have put it better myself.

34:15.529 --> 34:18.818
Yeah, so the kid is sitting
there, lying in my arms...

34:18.821 --> 34:21.489
sour smell of homemade
lasagna on his breath

34:21.493 --> 34:23.857
as he presses his cold,
clammy lips to my ear,

34:23.860 --> 34:25.827
and he...

34:25.830 --> 34:28.271
[SIGHS] He whispers it to me...

34:28.274 --> 34:31.039
right before he croaks.

34:31.042 --> 34:34.010
I'll never forget the words he utters.

34:34.013 --> 34:36.346
He says...

34:36.349 --> 34:38.283
"Tinkle, tinkle."

34:39.775 --> 34:43.076
[LAUGHING]

34:43.078 --> 34:46.052
[SCREAMING]

34:46.054 --> 34:50.291
Oh, I am going to get the words.

34:50.293 --> 34:52.494
Believe me.

34:52.496 --> 34:57.232
But I am going to take my time.

34:57.235 --> 34:59.435
I'm going to set an example with you.

34:59.438 --> 35:01.538
Do you want to know why? Not really.

35:01.541 --> 35:06.277
Because I am a professional.

35:06.280 --> 35:08.581
I take pride in my work.

35:08.584 --> 35:10.871
I approach my assignments

35:10.873 --> 35:13.674
with precision, discipline,

35:13.676 --> 35:16.443
and respect for my employers.

35:16.445 --> 35:20.047
You see, Sax, your reputation
precedes you as well.

35:20.049 --> 35:21.248
Mm?

35:21.250 --> 35:24.295
You seem to look at each new job

35:24.298 --> 35:27.032
as an opportunity to fulfill

35:27.035 --> 35:31.938
some half-acknowledged death wish.

35:31.941 --> 35:35.776
You just don't get it, do you, Smoothie?

35:35.779 --> 35:40.115
My life is an ever-swirling
toilet that just won't flush.

35:41.437 --> 35:43.770
I don't think I can die.

35:45.908 --> 35:47.507
We'll see.

35:48.610 --> 35:50.644
Music, please.

35:50.646 --> 35:52.979
<i>[COVER VERSION OF NEW
ORDER'S "BLUE MONDAY" PLAYS]</i>

35:52.981 --> 35:55.037
Wow. Was that as creepy as I felt?

35:55.040 --> 35:57.240
Creepy, right?

35:57.243 --> 35:58.576
[TOOL WHIRS]

35:58.579 --> 36:01.754
I am going to remove your penis

36:01.757 --> 36:03.982
in thin slices...

36:03.985 --> 36:05.785
like salami...

36:05.788 --> 36:08.894
just for starters.

36:08.897 --> 36:11.565
That's gonna take you a long time...

36:11.567 --> 36:13.600
if you know what I mean.

36:13.602 --> 36:15.502
He knows what I mean.

36:15.504 --> 36:18.705
[TOOL WHIRRING]

36:18.707 --> 36:21.942
[STRUGGLING]

36:21.944 --> 36:23.877
Oh, I don't think I can watch.

36:23.879 --> 36:25.495
Come on, Nick, do something!

36:25.498 --> 36:27.347
Well, you know, after a while,

36:27.349 --> 36:29.015
it just gets harder and harder

36:29.017 --> 36:30.959
to find a reason to keep on going.

36:30.962 --> 36:33.474
There's two kinds of people
in this godforsaken world,

36:33.477 --> 36:35.444
you worthless little maggot!

36:35.447 --> 36:36.913
Which kind do you want to be...

36:36.916 --> 36:39.984
A good apple or a road apple?

36:39.987 --> 36:42.062
[GROWLING]

36:42.064 --> 36:44.798
Oops! I pooped.

36:44.800 --> 36:47.801
Oh, for Christ sakes.

36:47.803 --> 36:50.871
<i>[ROCK MUSIC]</i>

36:50.874 --> 36:57.912
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:29.478 --> 37:32.045
Yeah, okay, well, I
think you made your point.

37:32.047 --> 37:34.448
So can we go back to saving Haley?

37:34.450 --> 37:36.416
Oh, is he going to be okay?

37:36.418 --> 37:38.427
[MAN GRUNTS]

37:38.430 --> 37:40.997
No, he is not gonna be okay.

37:41.000 --> 37:43.834
[GROANS SOFTLY]

37:45.794 --> 37:48.462
[CHOKING]

37:48.464 --> 37:50.564
[SIGHS]

37:50.566 --> 37:53.567
<i>[ELECTRONIC HOLIDAY MUSIC]</i>

37:53.569 --> 38:00.607
<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:04.213 --> 38:06.279
Hey, there.

38:06.281 --> 38:08.548
Didn't see you.

38:08.550 --> 38:13.920
<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:13.922 --> 38:16.060
Uh-huh.

38:16.063 --> 38:17.654
Oh, come on.

38:17.657 --> 38:21.059
Ah. Oh, yeah, papi.

38:21.062 --> 38:23.216
You like that?

38:23.219 --> 38:25.999
[FIRE EXTINGUISHERS DISPENSES]

38:26.001 --> 38:33.273
<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:39.515 --> 38:41.348
Ahh.

38:44.520 --> 38:46.720
[HYDRAULICS WHIRRING]

38:50.325 --> 38:52.158
I can explain.

38:52.160 --> 38:55.328
No, shoot to wound, man.
Blue wants him alive.

38:55.330 --> 38:59.165
Well, that's interesting.

38:59.167 --> 39:02.102
We'll tango later there, angry eyes.

39:02.104 --> 39:03.270
Gentlemen.

39:03.272 --> 39:06.573
[MEN SHOUTING]

39:06.575 --> 39:07.820
Let's go this way!

39:07.823 --> 39:10.257
- Get him!
- No, let's not go that way.

39:10.260 --> 39:12.527
Back off, or the horse gets it!

39:16.668 --> 39:18.200
On to the stairway!

39:18.203 --> 39:19.486
Follow me!

39:21.489 --> 39:23.389
Hold it!

39:23.392 --> 39:25.492
[MEN SHOUTING]

39:25.494 --> 39:28.495
<i>[TCHAIKOVSKY'S "DANCE OF
THE SUGAR PLUM FAIRY" PLAYS]</i>

39:28.497 --> 39:33.934
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:33.936 --> 39:37.137
I'm actually really good at this.

39:37.139 --> 39:39.973
Nice jacket.

39:39.975 --> 39:47.013
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:49.725 --> 39:51.759
[GASPS]

39:51.762 --> 39:53.553
I'm Dr.... [MUMBLES]

39:53.555 --> 39:56.723
And I need some... [MUMBLES]

39:56.725 --> 39:59.159
Rough day. What are you staring at?

39:59.161 --> 40:01.227
Tough tonsillectomy!

40:01.229 --> 40:03.163
Kid'll pull through,
though. I need coffee.

40:03.165 --> 40:10.170
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:11.340 --> 40:12.472
Ahh.

40:12.474 --> 40:14.574
Better?

40:14.576 --> 40:15.750
Actually, yeah.

40:15.753 --> 40:17.709
Then let's go save Haley! Come on!

40:17.712 --> 40:18.877
[GUNSHOT]

40:18.880 --> 40:20.086
Physical therapy, fifth floor!

40:20.089 --> 40:22.982
Get out of the way!

40:22.985 --> 40:25.919
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

40:25.921 --> 40:28.922
<i>[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]</i>

40:28.924 --> 40:35.395
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:35.397 --> 40:37.097
[ELEVATOR BELL DINGS]

40:37.099 --> 40:39.133
Yerks! More bad guys coming, Nick!

40:39.136 --> 40:41.436
I need less bad guys and
more good news out of you.

40:41.439 --> 40:43.936
We're in a family-sized
jar of pickles, Nick.

40:43.939 --> 40:46.106
I have no idea what that means.

40:46.108 --> 40:47.774
[STRAINS]

40:47.776 --> 40:50.076
[GRUNTING]

40:50.078 --> 40:52.554
What the heck, Nick?
There's no elevator!

40:52.557 --> 40:55.547
And you can't fly! Can you?

40:55.550 --> 40:57.359
Third floor.

40:57.362 --> 40:59.489
Oh, yeah. You got the loco eyes, buddy.

40:59.492 --> 41:01.420
You know what? You
can't help me save Haley

41:01.423 --> 41:02.648
if you're dead-zaroni!

41:02.651 --> 41:05.891
Yeah, and about this Haley
you keep yammering on about...

41:05.894 --> 41:09.187
to hell with her, and while
you're at it, to hell with you.

41:09.190 --> 41:11.203
[CRYING]

41:11.206 --> 41:13.440
Come on, don't do that.

41:13.443 --> 41:16.511
[SNIFFLES]

41:16.514 --> 41:18.080
How'd you know there were five?

41:21.610 --> 41:22.687
Huh?

41:22.690 --> 41:26.211
Back in my room. The
creepazoids coming for me.

41:26.214 --> 41:29.582
You're a manifestation, but...

41:29.584 --> 41:31.985
How'd you know there were five?

41:31.987 --> 41:34.621
- Yerk!
- [GUNSHOTS]

41:40.228 --> 41:44.140
[SIREN WAILING, GUNSHOTS]

41:44.143 --> 41:47.750
Whoo-hoo! Are we the best team or what?

41:47.753 --> 41:49.401
Ha ha!

41:49.404 --> 41:52.305
Oh, hey, Merry.

41:52.307 --> 41:55.742
- Nick.
- Yerks!

41:55.744 --> 41:58.111
- Can I borrow your car?
- [GULPS]

41:58.113 --> 42:01.715
- Son of a bitch.
- [CAR HORN HONKING]

42:01.717 --> 42:04.651
[HAPPY LAUGHING, TIRES SQUEALING]

42:04.653 --> 42:06.961
<i>[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]</i>

42:06.964 --> 42:08.578
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:08.581 --> 42:10.515
Go!

42:10.518 --> 42:12.524
Where we going, Nick,
huh? Where we going, huh?

42:12.527 --> 42:14.527
We? We ain't going nowhere.

42:14.529 --> 42:16.594
You heard that nice lady back there.

42:16.597 --> 42:19.015
I signed my own death warrant
when I iced Disco Mikey.

42:19.018 --> 42:20.852
Every scumbag in the city
will be looking for me

42:20.854 --> 42:21.828
if they're not already.

42:21.831 --> 42:24.242
- Eh, I mean, yeah, but...
- Yeah, but nothing.

42:24.245 --> 42:26.045
I'm getting the hell out of Dodge.

42:26.048 --> 42:27.898
[TAPPING HOOF RAPIDLY]

42:27.901 --> 42:30.610
Quit your tap dancing.
You're ruining the dashboard.

42:30.612 --> 42:32.412
I didn't want to tell you, Nick.

42:32.414 --> 42:33.648
So then don't.

42:33.651 --> 42:35.318
I was afraid of scaring you away.

42:35.321 --> 42:36.787
After all, you left her once before.

42:36.790 --> 42:39.257
[TIRES SQUEALING]

42:39.260 --> 42:41.354
Maybe you just don't want to be a daddy.

42:41.356 --> 42:43.367
What are you yammering on about?

42:43.370 --> 42:45.136
Why do you think I picked you, Nick?

42:45.139 --> 42:46.892
I don't know. Lucky, I guess.

42:46.895 --> 42:48.664
You can say that again.

42:48.674 --> 42:51.429
Nick, Haley is your daughter.

42:55.170 --> 42:57.771
[HORN BLARING]

43:02.082 --> 43:05.116
[COUGHING]

43:05.119 --> 43:07.019
<i>[HOLIDAY MUSIC]</i>

43:07.022 --> 43:11.656
♪ Toy land, toy land ♪

43:11.659 --> 43:15.360
♪ Little girl and boy land ♪

43:15.363 --> 43:17.263
[CRIES]

